    "_postman_id": "98a716af-00ac-416c-9253-2039b8f88db1",
    "name": "Lattice",
    "description": "## Lattice\n\nThis collection covers the core API workflows for the **Lattice** event management platform. It provides endpoints to manage events and handle user bookings and attendance.\n\n### Endpoints\n\n| Method | Endpoint | Description |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| POST | `/api/events` | Create a new event |\n| POST | `/api/bookings` | Book a ticket for an event |\n| POST | `/api/events/:id/attendance` | Mark attendance for an event |\n| GET | `/api/bookings` | Retrieve all bookings for a user |\n| GET | `/api/events` | Retrieve a list of all events |\n\n### Variables\n\nThe collection uses the following environment variables:\n\n- `{{url}}` — Base URL for the events service\n    \n- `http://localhost:3000` — Base URL for the bookings and attendance service (port 3000)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "39105518"
  },
